          <h2>Platform Board</h2>
          <p>The Platform Board provides specific governance about infrastructure and platform choices, especially around the use of Cloud platforms. The model is driven by the result of a <a href="https://digital.nhs.uk/data-and-information/looking-after-information/data-security-and-information-governance/nhs-and-social-care-data-off-shoring-and-the-use-of-public-cloud-services/health-and-social-care-data-risk-model">cloud risk assessment</a> that programmes undertake.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>For activities at Classes I and II: TRG must be approached for approval directly.</li>
            <li>For activities at Classes III, IV and V: Platform Board must be approached for approval, and will expect activities to have been supported through TRG.</li>
          </ul>

